title: The Gits - Punk Rock
description:
The Gits are a punk rock band from Seattle that broke up in 1993. More people need to know about them because they are incredibly awesome. 

This isn&#039;t their complete discography but its close enough. The albums not included are just originals. These are the new higher quality releases.
